        "setup": "Complete Yoti onboarding, then generate your credentials in the Yoti Hub/portal. The docs describe the auth inputs as an SDK ID plus a PEM private key generated from the Hub, and the onboarding page is the setup entry point: [Facial Age Estimation onboarding](https://developers.yoti.com/age-estimation/onboarding). For Identity Verification API auth, use your backend SDK to sign requests with the private key and send the resulting digest in `X-Yoti-Auth-Digest`; include `sdkId`, `nonce`, and `timestamp` query parameters as required by the API docs: [Identity Verification API](https://developers.yoti.com/identity-verification-api).",
